Go to utils

baseUrl.js




const baseUrl =
  process.env.NODE_ENV === "production"
    ? "https://deployment-url.now.sh"
    : "http://localhost:3000";

export default baseUrl;

2-Go to the index.js (where Home is)

import baseUrl

-replace the localhost part of the url to :

`${baseUrl}/api/product`

3-Go to the product.js
